         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Determine the processing schedule for automated entries, and then create the entries.  The frequency of automated entry processing is usually driven by the reporting requirements from the General Ledger. The calculation criteria and schedule will need to be reviewed periodically to ensure the integrity of generated transactions posted to the GL."/>
